Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You raised your price again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think your\Nplace charges a bit much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.02,0:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise it again and I'll stop buying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?\NIt's just a paper or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not when you're buying it everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for\Nyou to save up money
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to buy your village back\Nfrom Arlong now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or to be so obsessive about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that everything's over,\NI'm going to earn money for me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna be some poor\Npirate who can't even dress up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of developing\Nmy special Tabasco Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eyeful of this\Nwill make any bad guy--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--C'mon! Just one!\N--Water! Water! Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nami-san's tangerine orchard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone lay a finger on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Your love\Nsecurity is infallible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:03:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ol' Sanji's letting himself be used...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Just one tangerine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a cheapskate, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, oh, well! I'm happy now, anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world sure is a turbulent place.\NAnother coup in Villa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bounty! Straw Hat Luffy\NBecomes Known to the World"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:58.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at the very least, they're now\Ntoo much for our branches to handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even before\Nforming his pirate group,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he defeated Navy Branch\NCaptain Axe-Hand Morgan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's showed no signs\Nof slowing down since.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy the Clown, 15 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Fleet Commodore,\NDon Krieg. 17 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Pirate,\NSaw-Tooth Arlong. 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These major pirates have all crossed\Nthe big 10 million Berry mark
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the East Blue, where the average\Nbounty is 3 million Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they've all been taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million Berries as a starting\Nbounty is globally unprecedented,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is not an\Nexcessively high amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be best to nip such\Nseeds of villainy early on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:05:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before they have a\Nchance to get out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who wants\Nto run away, do so now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bastion of peace will not tolerate\Nany weakness in this pirate age!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The public's weakness and feebleness\Nis not a sin! We have justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is tenacious evil on the seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we, the Navy, must drive\Nit away with utmost force!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of absolute justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:49.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely Usopp-san\Nfacing the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you\Nmention it, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! You're looking\Na lot better, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of story\Nshall I tell you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san is moving toward his dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving toward my dream of being\Na doctor to help everyone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that someday, somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my dream and Usopp-san's\Ndream will come together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:17.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chore Boy"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally... Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! You've finally\Nset foot into your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy! The man who's\Ngonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the next time we meet,\Nwe may be enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it so I can\Nachieve my own goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... do you know the All Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the damn things\Nyou've done for me all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're wanted criminals now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dead or alive"...\N"30 million Berries"...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says I'm 30 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I'm gonna be seen around\Nthe world! Girls might fall for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They put Long-nose\Nin but left me out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!\NI don't see you anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the back of your head.\NThat's nothing to brag about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so glum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get on these without being\Ncaptain if you get more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep on tryin' hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rush into the Grand Line, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet again, you guys don't understand\Nthe seriousness of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means our lives are in danger now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be taking it easy\Nand relaxing in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that amount, I bet\NHeadquarters will take action,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and strong bounty hunters\Nwon't leave us alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be on a completely\Ndifferent level than everyone so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:11:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go! Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Cheap booze\Nmakes me feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I long for the old days
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was surrounded by\Nbeautiful women and fine wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My one encounter with that\Nhorrible waiter changed my fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tarnishing the Navy's name lost\Nme my rank of Navy HQ Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and put me in charge of this hunk\Nof junk in the middle of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Former Lieutenant Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya want?! You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have a new wanted poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Just leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it means anything to us,\Nseeing as we're all the way out--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This face... I've seen it\Nsomewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen that pirate flag before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Iron Fist Fullbody,\NLieutenant at Navy Headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your captain?! State your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just made our pirate flag\Nthe day before yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God has given me a chance to climb\Nout of this hellish pit of boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can catch that brat easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll use that feat to get my\Nrank of Navy HQ Lieutenant back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! We're going into battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle? Where are we gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... The sea restaurant, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! A restaurant!\N--Awesome! A big feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's the captain's treat!\N--Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, you got it all wrong!\N--Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to port! Our target's\Nright in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think some pirates\Nattacked it? That warship is scrapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice of the Navy to toss\Nits scrapped ships into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a scrapped ship!\NDo you guys got knotholes for eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten what\NIron Fist Fullbody looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're that navy\Nguy from sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stranded? Want us to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fooling around! Our meeting\Nhere spells the end of your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy! You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's a good\Npicture of me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of the back of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "Dead or alive"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim the turret!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the noise? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're gonna shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're aiming right at us! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Leave it to me!\NI'll bounce it back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. Let me handle this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah, yeah! You stay back here!\N--H-How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you mess things up.\NC'mon! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremble and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's all this damn noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother people\Nwhen they're napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more\Nwhere that came from! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? This is bad.\N--It is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There were cracks in the cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's definitely bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare mock the power\Nof a former Navy HQ Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to\Nfight you hand-to-hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some real balls, pickin'\Na fight during mealtime, tough guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't got any soup bowls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plannin' to lick\Nthe deck or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that waiter doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was nothing but talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as damn wimpy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you guys! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I can't even relax\Nand read a newspaper here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I'm finished\Npreparing your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! I'm starving!\NLet's eat! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye! Why the hell are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. I have no business with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camping on an island like this...\NWhat a carefree man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Hawk-Eye.\NWhat a rare visitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feelin' so good at the moment...\NHave you come to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any intention\Nof settling things with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that you've lost your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found an interesting pirate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was suddenly reminded\Nof a story you used to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A story about an interesting boy\Nfrom a certain small village...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've made it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Hawk-Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:19:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't just let you leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That so, Hawk-Eye?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Drink up! Drink up!\NToday's a celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had a hangover?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!\NIt's a celebratory drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, now! C'mon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drink it straight down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.83,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like ya!\NLet's drink! Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait! Boss! You said you felt\Nsick 'cause you drank too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! I can't not drink\Non a joyous day like today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is still high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's party hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy's a wanted man now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, maybe a great pirate\Nwill've come from this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so good about a criminal\Ncoming from our village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Every last one of them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mayor! Luffy looks so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.82,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is his dream. Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams... Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally nearing the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the only way into it\Nis through Reverse Mountain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.\NCan't we just sail straight into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what the geezer told me,\Nthat's the only way boats can enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's supposedly dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know any more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason for that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I got it!\NThen let's head straight into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you even paying attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it'd feel way better\Ngoing straight into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to you makes me\Nfeel like I'm gonna go crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's stop at\Nan island first and get meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a famous city on\Nthis island... Loguetown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loguetown?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it famous for its meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the city\Nof the beginning and the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the town where Gold Roger,\Nthe old King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was born... and executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town where the\NKing of the Pirates died...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the town where\Nthe man who got the One Piece--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything this world has to offer--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was born and then died!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's that\Nred-nosed thing called again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, that guy with the big nose!\N--Oh, him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Boogey or Baggy\Nthe Brown or something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Buggy the Clown! Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what\Nhappened to him after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.02,0:24:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chase Straw Hat!\NLittle Buggy's Big Adventure"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
